{"tid":2095054,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【土司】陳弘毅指若文章不涉倡武力違法手段　則不構成顛覆","createTime":"2020-07-05T07:21:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T08:05:03.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ca2fc7f6354ede2b2afb47e243a25f7ed4ae6a57","tid":2095054,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T07:21:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535876-20200705.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535876-20200705.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=yjoviXv3QiMsqLwchXvj3yUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=55988ae7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535876-20200705.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=b98d299e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535876-20200705.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n基本法委員會委員陳弘毅表示，若有人寫文章煽動他人改變中國或香港政治制度，當中不涉及鼓勵用武力或違法手段，相信並不構成《港區國安法》的顛覆國家政權罪。<br />\n<br />\n就「8.31太子站打死人」引發特區居民對政府的憎恨的說法，陳弘毅表示，並不構成《港區國安法》有關勾結外國勢力的罪行，因為在香港發放虛假消息並不違法，亦要視乎有關人士有否請求外國勢力等。"},{"pid":"3e0c5cd6c4873fad7bf95ec77f9f116adb6a2301","tid":2095054,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T07:22:19.000Z","msg":"陳弘毅自己何不寫一篇試吓發表？"},{"pid":"cffdfbbbf67d806ff6950b1fb61d833a4afdbda6","tid":2095054,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T07:26:17.000Z","msg":"講明係你個人觀點咋 唔代表支共立場呀"},{"pid":"19d0ba2b17435f314cf2c4d2171536e5ef0defac","tid":2095054,"uid":54721,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T07:27:36.000Z","msg":"搵個話得事既黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bec221b5a35b007dbd65c80d0678bf623dcac003","tid":2095054,"uid":41116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T07:27:49.000Z","msg":"你地呢班撚樣比完advice未<br />\n幾撚時輪到你講野"},{"pid":"9031e72036dc6963a0aed8ad23765ae47cf0e065",